    <title>Python爬虫实战——外网爬取加页面滚动</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/Python%E7%88%AC%E8%99%AB%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%A4%96%E7%BD%91%E7%88%AC%E5%8F%96%E5%8A%A0%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E6%BB%9A%E5%8A%A8%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/Python%E7%88%AC%E8%99%AB%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%A4%96%E7%BD%91%E7%88%AC%E5%8F%96%E5%8A%A0%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E6%BB%9A%E5%8A%A8%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA/</id>
    <published>2023-06-09T04:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2023-06-10T07:31:22.914Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="一项目背景介绍">一、项目背景介绍</h1><p>我们想要研究国外的华语报刊和内地普通话报刊在词汇使用上的异同，因此首先我们需要对不同国家的报刊资料进行爬取。我们选定的国家为马来西亚，想要爬取的报刊网址为https://www.sinchew.com.my/和https://www.chinapress.com.my/，我们会在这两个网站上分别摘取一些文章，使得文章总篇数为100篇左右。同时对于内地的报刊，我们选用的是http://www.people.com.cn/和http://paper.news.cn/，同样爬取100篇左右的内容即可。几个网站的网页分别展示如下：</p><figure><img src="/Python%E7%88%AC%E8%99%AB%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%A4%96%E7%BD%91%E7%88%AC%E5%8F%96%E5%8A%A0%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E6%BB%9A%E5%8A%A8%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA/Blog\source_posts\pic\spider\sinchew_first_page.png" alt="星洲网首页图片"><figcaption aria-hidden="true">星洲网首页图片</figcaption></figure><figure><img src="/Python%E7%88%AC%E8%99%AB%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%A4%96%E7%BD%91%E7%88%AC%E5%8F%96%E5%8A%A0%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E6%BB%9A%E5%8A%A8%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA/Blog\source_posts\pic\spider\chinapress_first_page.png" alt="中国报首页"><figcaption aria-hidden="true">中国报首页</figcaption></figure><figure><img src="/Python%E7%88%AC%E8%99%AB%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%A4%96%E7%BD%91%E7%88%AC%E5%8F%96%E5%8A%A0%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E6%BB%9A%E5%8A%A8%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA/Blog\source_posts\pic\spider\people_first_page.png" alt="人民网首页"><figcaption aria-hidden="true">人民网首页</figcaption></figure><figure><img src="/Python%E7%88%AC%E8%99%AB%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%A4%96%E7%BD%91%E7%88%AC%E5%8F%96%E5%8A%A0%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E6%BB%9A%E5%8A%A8%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA/Blog\source_posts\pic\spider\xinhua_first_page.png" alt="新华社首页"><figcaption aria-hidden="true">新华社首页</figcaption></figure><h1 id="sinchew网站爬虫实战">sinchew网站爬虫实战</h1><p>第一个爬虫我将以requests+bs4为例做展示，需要导入的库为：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> requests</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> bs4 <span class="keyword">import</span> BeautifulSoup</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>首先我们实现一个最基础的获取网页的框架：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">url1 = <span class="string">r&quot;https://www.sinchew.com.my&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># get html using header</span></span><br><span class="line">headers = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;User-Agent&quot;</span>:<span class="string">&quot;Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/114.0.0.0 Safari/537.36&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Accept&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Accept-Language&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;en-us&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Connection&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;keep-alive&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Accept-Charset&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;GB2312,utf-8;q=0.7,*;q=0.7&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">r = requests.get(url1, headers=headers)</span><br><span class="line">soup = BeautifulSoup(r.content, <span class="string">&quot;html.parser&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>我们将会发现以上代码是无法获得对应网站的响应的，无论当前主机上是否开启了代理，这是因为这个网站实际上是需要翻墙才能登录的，因此我们需要先考虑怎么使得爬虫能够识别代理。以我使用的Clash为例，我们可以从Clash的常规页面的第一项端口看到，这里使用的端口是7890：</p><figure><img src="/Python%E7%88%AC%E8%99%AB%E5%AE%9E%E6%88%98%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E5%A4%96%E7%BD%91%E7%88%AC%E5%8F%96%E5%8A%A0%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2%E6%BB%9A%E5%8A%A8%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA/Blog\source_posts\pic\spider\Clash.png" alt="Clash常规页面"><figcaption aria-hidden="true">Clash常规页面</figcaption></figure><p>于是我们应该将以上代码修改为：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">url1 = <span class="string">r&quot;https://www.sinchew.com.my/category/%E5%85%A8%E5%9B%BD/%E5%8D%B3%E6%97%B6%E5%9B%BD%E5%86%85/&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># get html using header</span></span><br><span class="line">headers = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;User-Agent&quot;</span>:<span class="string">&quot;Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/114.0.0.0 Safari/537.36&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Accept&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;text/html,application/xhtml+xml,application/xml;q=0.9,*/*;q=0.8&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Accept-Language&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;en-us&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Connection&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;keep-alive&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;Accept-Charset&quot;</span> : <span class="string">&quot;GB2312,utf-8;q=0.7,*;q=0.7&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">proxies=&#123;<span class="string">&#x27;http&#x27;</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;http://127.0.0.1:7890&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;https&#x27;</span>: <span class="string">&#x27;http://127.0.0.1:7890&#x27;</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line">r = requests.get(url1, headers=headers, proxies=proxies)</span><br><span class="line">soup = BeautifulSoup(r.content, <span class="string">&quot;html.parser&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>实际上也就是添加了proxies参数而已，在这里proxies最后两项的7890应该修改为你对应的端口。</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;h1 id=&quot;一项目背景介绍&quot;&gt;一、项目背景介绍&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;我们想要研究国外的华语报刊和内地普通话报刊在词汇使用上的异同，因此首先我们需要对不同国家的报刊资料进行爬取。我们选定的国家为马来西亚，想要爬取的报刊网址为https://www.sinchew.com.my/和</summary>
      
    
    
    
    
